				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "(script comment: it is repeated, but I don't want it to be culled out)\r\nThis occurs as the player approaches the scene. Locke and Marrick are arguing with two druid guards - trying to get in. Their daughter is inside but they are being denied entrance.Tensions are high and voices are raised. This is a tense exchange. "
